<!-- 关联公司 --><div class="newsflash-company" id="newsflash-company"></div></div>]]></description><guid isPermaLink="false">12329540</guid><pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 14:52:52 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>DeepSeek获顶级域名ai.com认可</title><link>https://www.jiemian.com/article/12329557.html</link><description><![CDATA[<div class="article-content"><p>记者发现，现在在浏览器输入ai.com，将直接重定向至DeepSeek官网(https://chat.deepseek.com/)。据了解，ai.com域名的定位被视作前沿AI的象征，此前这一域名曾长期被定位到ChatGPT和马斯克的xAI官网。（中新财经）</p>
